picked you out as a potential victim.

553
00:38:33,653 --> 00:38:37,362
You were rich, bitter, angry, obsessed.

554
00:38:38,453 --> 00:38:40,603
You were ripe to be plucked.

555
00:38:40,933 --> 00:38:42,571
You're a con man.

556
00:38:44,373 --> 00:38:48,048
