I won't be a part of it.

557
00:38:59,559 --> 00:39:00,708
Wait.

558
00:39:02,519 --> 00:39:04,475
You were setting me up.

559
00:39:04,959 --> 00:39:06,028
I was.

560
00:39:06,119 --> 00:39:09,429
You con people for money,
that's what you're saying?

561
00:39:10,159 --> 00:39:12,468
You're all the same, all of you.

562
00:39:13,919 --> 00:39:15,193
Â£200,000.

563
00:39:15,719 --> 00:39:18,631
- I'll give you Â£200,000.
- There is no spa.

564
00:39:19,239 --> 00:39:22,754
Who said anything about a spa?
I want you to destroy my ex-husband.

565
00:39:23,319 --> 00:39:25,071
A rat to catch a rat.

566
00:39:25,159 --> 00:39:29,232
- Don't do this.
- Â£250,000. What's your price, scumbag?

567
00:39:29,919 --> 00:39:31,398
