568
00:39:32,199 --> 00:39:34,190
No, it's not what we do.

569
00:39:34,439 --> 00:39:36,430
It's one thing
conning a nasty piece of work.

570
00:39:36,519 --> 00:39:38,589
She is a nasty piece of work.

571
