575
00:39:50,239 --> 00:39:53,037
ran off with a younger model,
and promptly got her pregnant.

576
00:39:53,119 --> 00:39:55,030
- You haven't even met him.
- I know his type.

577
00:39:55,119 --> 00:39:56,552
Then why are we talking about it?

578
00:39:56,639 --> 00:39:59,870
If he's that bad, he doesn't sound
any different from any other con.

579
00:39:59,959 --> 00:40:01,312
And there's June to think about.

580
00:40:01,399 --> 00:40:04,311
No, she wouldn't want us to do anything
just because of her.

581
00:40:04,399 --> 00:40:05,991
I would, though.

582
00:40:09,559 --> 00:40:11,072
Okay, then we have to move fast.

583
00:40:11,159 --> 00:40:12,990
