584
00:40:13,079 --> 00:40:14,876
- That's when we get him.
- What's the in?

585
00:40:14,959 --> 00:40:17,712
I have no idea.
He's a very careful man, by all accounts.

586
00:40:17,799 --> 00:40:20,393
- Women?
- He's had two in his whole life.

587
00:40:20,479 --> 00:40:21,468
Revenge.

588
00:40:21,559 --> 00:40:24,312
