599
00:40:56,759 --> 00:40:59,193
- So what do we do now?
- We need proof.

600
00:41:04,959 --> 00:41:06,915
No. No way.

601
00:41:06,999 --> 00:41:09,559
Come on, you did it once.
What's the difference?

602
00:41:09,639 --> 00:41:11,675
I didn't know she was a hooker then, did I?

603
00:41:12,159 --> 00:41:14,229
